These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, biathlon, rugby
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, roller, helicopter
1. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere between the person who's sport is cycling and the person driving the roller##7
2. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the right of the person driving the roller##5
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the right of the person driving the roller##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3   |
| Sport   | rugby | biathlon | cycling |
| Transport           | roller  | helicopter     | skateboard  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-2::.
3 different pets are kept: hamster, guinea-pig, ferret
City: rome, hannover, liverpool
1. the person traveling to rome is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the hamster is somewhere between the owner of the ferret and the person traveling to hannover##7
3. the person traveling to rome is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |   3    |
| Pet   | guinea-pig | hamster | ferret |
| City     | hannover       | liverpool     | rome |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-3::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, daffodil, daisy
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, fantasy, sports
1. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere between the person who growsamaryllis and the person watching musical movies##7
2. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |   3    |
| Flower    | amaryllis | daffodil | daisy  |
| Movie-Genre   | sports  | fantasy  | musical |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-4::.
3 different pets are kept: ferret, horse, fish
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, bongani, baccarat
1. the owner of the ferret is somewhere between the baccarat-smoker and the owner of the horse##7
2. the bongani-smoker is not the owner of the ferret##6
3. the baccarat-smoker is somewhere to the right of the bongani-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |        2        |      3      |
| Pet           | horse | ferret | fish     |
| Cigar   | bongani    | pall-mall          | baccarat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, cooking, woodworking
There are 3 different favourite colors: blood-red, chestnut, ivory
1. the person who likes chestnut is somewhere between the person who likes ivory and the person who's hobby is cooking##7
2. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person who likes chestnut##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Hobby   | hiking      | woodworking     | cooking   |
| Color     | ivory | chestnut | blood-red |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-6::.
3 different games are played: bridge, backgammon, whist
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: thriller, spy, sports
1. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person watching spy movies##3
2. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching thriller movies##5
3. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
4. the person playing backgammon is somewhere between the person watching sports movies and the person playing bridge##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
| Game   | whist    | backgammon     | bridge     |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | spy | thriller |

