.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-7::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: orchid, balloon-flower, rose
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, coffee, lemonade
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere between the person who growsorchid and the person drinking soy-milk##7
3. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who growsrose##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| Flower     | rose       | balloon-flower      | orchid       |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | lemonade | coffee |

