.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-9::.
There 3 different types of food: strawberry, raspberry, artichoke
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, sprite, coffee
1. the person drinking coffee is not the person eating artichoke##6
2. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
3. the person drinking juice is somewhere between the person drinking sprite and the person eating raspberry##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2    |    3    |
| Food   | raspberry | artichoke | strawberry   |
| Beverage     | coffee    | juice  | sprite |

