.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-10::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, july, december
3 different pets are kept: hamster, hedgehog, snake
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
2. the owner of the snake is the person who's birthday is in july##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in july and the owner of the hedgehog##7

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Birthday   | july   | december    | may |
| Pet      | snake | hamster | hedgehog |

