.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-12::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: red, turquise, chestnut
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, mirinda, hot-chocolate
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere between the person drinking mirinda and the person who likes red##7
3. the person who likes turquise is somewhere to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3     |
| Color          | red  | chestnut       | turquise     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | iced-tea | mirinda |

