2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere between the person who's sport is parkour and the person watching time-travel movies##7
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |  3   |
| Movie-Genre      | mystery     | horror | time-travel |
| Sport   | parkour | weightlifting    | snowboarding |

