2. the siglo-smoker is somewhere between the fonseca-smoker and the person who's hobby is reading##7
3. the siglo-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| Cigar   | fonseca      | siglo     | dannemann |
| Hobby        | magic-tricks | sudoku | reading    |

 